extraction.query:
SELECT
    ID.DOMAIN_NAME,
    ID.ITINERARY_GID,
    ID.ITINERARY_XID,
    ITD.LEG_GID,
    ITD.SEQUENCE_NO,
    L.LEG_NAME,
    L.LEG_TYPE,
    L.EQUIPMENT_GROUP_PROFILE_GID,
    L.MODE_PROFILE_GID,
    L.DEST_LOCATION_GID,
    L.RATE_OFFERING_GID,
    L.AUTO_CONSOLIDATION_TYPE
FROM
    ITINERARY ID,
    ITINERARY_DETAIL ITD,
    LEG L
WHERE
    ID.ITINERARY_GID = ITD.ITINERARY_GID
    AND ITD.LEG_GID = L.LEG_GID
    AND ID.DOMAIN_NAME = 'BAU'
ORDER BY
    ID.ITINERARY_XID,
    ITD.SEQUENCE_NO
